ack;font-size:14px;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">新闻背景：</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:18pt;text-indent:21pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:small;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">锦湖轮胎被央视曝光事件</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;line-height:18pt;text-indent:21pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:small;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:14px;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">●3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Arial\',\'sans-serif\';color:black;font-size:14px;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\" lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:14px;mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"